## Summary Scorecard

| Dimension | Grade | Key Strengths | Key Weaknesses |
|-----------|-------|---------------|----------------|
| **Security & Privacy** | **B-** | CSP headers, XSS sanitization, RBAC on most actions, rate limiting, file upload validation, audit logging | Exposed secrets, insecure cookie, CSP `unsafe-eval`, missing auth on 2 actions |
| **Development Practices** | **B** | TypeScript strict mode, Zod validation on critical paths, clean schema types | `as any` usage, bloated components, duplicated upload code, FormData casting |
| **Performance** | **B-** | `Promise.all` for parallel queries, transaction mode pooling | Unoptimized images, missing DB indexes, in-memory rate limiter, dead query |
| **Usability & A11y** | **C+** | Responsive design with Tailwind, semantic footer | Missing ARIA labels, empty href="#", non-functional payment options |
| **Privacy & Compliance** | **C** | `.env*` in .gitignore, Clerk handles auth tokens | No right-to-deletion, insecure cookie flags, no cookie consent, indefinite PII storage |
| **Architecture** | **B+** | Clean separation of actions/components/lib, Drizzle ORM, proper schema design | Single DB client config, console-only audit logging, no route groups |

